title: Crazy Covid stories with Ricci Armani
description:
This week Joe takes a trip to a naked beach with his great and hilarious muggle-friend Ricci Armani! Then they discuss all the things you can find at gas stations to put in your body before Ricci gets a mind-blowing look behind the teaching curtain as Joe shares Socialite Nation's craziest Covid teaching stories.
